sect1.para:
The GNU compiler collection version 7 as provided with &slehpca;
and the MPI flavors Open MPI v.3, Open MPI v.4, MPICH, and MVAPICH2 are
currently supported.

sect2.para:
The Open Community Runtime project is an application-building framework
that explores methods for high-core-count programming with focus on &hpca;
applications.
